Kevin J. O'Connor (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kevin_J._O%27Connor_(actor) 0 Kevin James O'Connor (born November 15, 1963) is an American actor. O'Connor is known for portraying character roles in major studio films such as There Will Be Blood, The Mummy, Lord of Illusions, F/X2 and Van Helsing. He is a favorite of writer/director Stephen Sommers, who usually casts him in his films. Kevin_James_O'Connor ( born November_15_,_1963 ) is an_American_actor .
